What is the dimension of the weight bench preacher pad? Is it wide enough? 
Hello, the preacher pad measures 18 inches, which is 3"-5" wider than similar products, providing a wide enough range for exercise. 
How to better perform leg extension exercises? 
Hello, if you are tall, we recommend removing the preacher pad for more exercise space.

features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, leg extensions, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Equipped with a 210lb weight stack, this curl machine provides a wide range of resistance levels, and is suitable for a home gym setup. Also upgradable to 310 lb stack.

DUAL EXERCISE CAPABILITY: The Easy pull pin design seamlessly switches between leg extensions to strengthen your quadriceps and leg curls to focus on your hamstrings, delivering a complete leg workout on one machine. Improve leg strength, enhance muscle definition, and train athletic performance, this machine supports various lower body exercises for overall leg development.

ERGONOMIC DESIGN FOR MAXIMUM COMFORT: Features 7 position adjustments on the back pad and leg hold down to fit all size users. The 8" foam rollers and durafirm pads add comfort to each exercise. aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Do you know the benefits of stretching? 
Increases your flexibility - Regular stretching can help increase your flexibility, which is crucial for your overall health. Not only can improved flexibility help you to perform everyday activities with relative ease, but it can also help delay the reduced mobility that can come with aging.
Increases your range of motion - Being able to move a joint through its full range of motion gives you more freedom of movement. Stretching on a regular basis can help increase your range of motion.
Improves your performance in physical activities - Stretches prior to physical activities can help you prepare your muscles Trusted Source for the activity. It can also help improve your performance in an athletic event or exercise.
Increases blood flow to your muscles - Performing stretches on a regular basis can improve your circulationTrusted Source. Improved circulation increases blood flow to your muscles, which can shorten your recovery time and reduce muscle soreness.
Improves your posture - Muscle imbalances are common and can lead to poor posture. Strengthening and stretching specific muscle groups can reduce musculoskeletal pain and encourage proper alignment. That, in turn, can help improve your posture.
Helps to heal and prevent leg pain - Tight muscles can lead to a decrease in your range of motion. When this happens, you increase the likelihood of straining the muscles in your leg. Stretching can help heal an existing leg injury by stretching the muscles, it can also help prevent future leg pain by strengthening your leg muscles and reducing your risk for muscle strain.
Can calm your mind and great for stress relief - Participating in a regular stretching program not only helps increase your flexibility, but it can also calm your mind. While you stretch, focus on mindfulness and meditation exercises, which give you a break and reduce your stress.
Helps decrease tension headaches - Tension and stress headaches can interfere with your daily life. In addition to a proper diet, adequate hydration, and plenty of rest, stretching may help reduce the tension you feel from headaches.

High-Quality Square Stainless Steel & Comfortable Non-slip Handle 
Our leg stretcher is made of High-quality square stainless steel.

Other competing products weight is only 1KG, very light, it will cause the head of leg stretcher lifted easily, which is not conducive to use. 
Our Comfortable Non-slip Handle is air permeability and abrasion resistance. It creates a comfortable grip for manipulating the stretcher and a comfortable resting point on your feet, ankles for increasing your stretch. 
6 speed adjustable & Unique button design 
Each pole has six holes that you adjust to find the perfect, comfortable stretching length level or increase it to get a deeper stretch.
If you’re a beginner at stretching, the best way is to start at the bottom hole which gives you the easiest stretch.
After some weeks, you can move up the holes on the leg stretcher for high stretching. It will help you gradually increase the flexibility.
Some Professional Tips: 
When you hunch or round your lower back while stretching, it breaks the balance of your muscles in the back. It can lead to cramps and spasms in the back. It also puts your spine out of alignment. Do not round or arch your back.
Sit comfortably on the floor before starting to use your bar stretcher for legs. The best way is to sit on your ischium bone in the pelvic region to prevent hunching your back. 
When you are stretching and your legs suddenly begin to burn or pain uncontrollable, it is a sign that you overstretched. Unless you take a break for a day or two, there are high chances you might injure yourself.
If you’re a beginner, it is best to start it slow. keep the stretch training 3 or 4 times per week. 
Relax and relived your legs and shoulders in between the exercise.
How to use a leg stretcher? 
Step 1: Warm-up. It will help you increase the heat of your body. Example: walk, run or other exercises to wake up your leg muscles.
Step 2: Sit on the floor and stretch your legs. Keep both the feet on the both sides of the leg split stretcher. Lean forward from the hips.
Step 3: Pull the central bar close to you. Hold the pull for up to a minute. Contract the leg muscles by pushing both legs together. Hold for up to 10 seconds. Hold for one minute. Repeat until you can’t increase your stretch. 
Step 4: Once the stretch is over, breath in and out deeply so that your body temperature and heart palpitations come down.
Step 5: The adjustable height or length of a bar stretcher is useful for improving your stretches. To do so, remove and re-adjust the central bar by going to the lower length hole. Once you have perfected this length, go to the next one and so on.
Portable & Unisex & Our Advice 
We also provide you with a storage bag, you can take the leg stretcher anywhere. 
This leg stretcher can be used by men and women without any problems.
Kids also can use it (Note:Children above one meter can use it)
Our Leg Stretcher is excellent to train yourself to split your legs from 45-90-135-180 degrees tactically. Everyone can use it!
We recommend you to record yourself doing splits and watch the video to see how much you have improved.
Stretch while watching tv, movie, or listening to music can make stretching more enjoyable.
Never wear tight clothes.
We also provide you with 1 Yoga Stretch Strap. Look this picture! 
Questions & Answers 
Q: Which sports is this product good for? 
A: Martial Arts, Karate, Muay Thai, Taekwondo, Sanda, Dance, Gymnastic, Running, Fitness or any sports that require a certain level of flexibility. 
Q: How long does it takes to get the first result? 
A: If you train 15-30 minutes everyday, we think you will probably have great results after 30 days. 
Q: Can the leg stretcher stretch my hamstrings? 
A: Sure, you can stretch your hamstrings with this product by doing forward bends on each of your legs. 
Q: I am a tall or short person, can I use it? Is it suitable for kids? 
A: Yes, you can adjust it according to your height. It is also suitable for kids above 1 meter height.

It relaxes leg muscles, promotes leg blood circulation, burns calories, improves cardiovascular health, strengthens muscles, and helps legs recover quickly, making it an excellent choice.

3 Exercise Modes: In non - electric mode, move forward without a power cable. Auto mode has 3 levels (P1, P2, P3), running 30 minutes automatically with machine - selected speed and directions. Adjust P1 - P3 via the Auto button. In HR (manual) mode, set speed (1 - 12), directions (forward/reverse), and workout time (15 - 30 minutes) by pressing the manual button on the machine or using the remote control.

12 Adjustable Speeds & 2 Movement Directions (Forward and Reverse): These diverse options can significantly improve your exercise routine. Whether you're doing rehabilitation exercises, trying to strengthen your leg muscles, or relax your foot joints, you can easily choose the speed and mode that are right for you.

Intelligent Control System: This seated exercise machine has two control methods - the large LCD touch screen and the remote control. The remote control is great as it enables you to adjust the machine without bending, protecting your waist and back, ideal for the elderly and those with limited mobility. Note: The remote control requires 2 AAA batteries not included due to logistics, so you need to prepare them. Also, don't use the machine while standing.

Lifetime After - Sales Service: We offer an outstanding after - sales service. Every owner of the DamKee under desk elliptical machine is eligible for a three - month return service and lifetime after - sales support. If you have any questions regarding the seated elliptical, you can contact us through Amazon messages. Our professional customer service team is committed to providing you with a 100% satisfactory solution within 24 hours.

Quiet Motor & Portable: Enjoy leg exercises while working, watching TV, reading, or during a meeting without any worry of being interrupted or disturbing others, thanks to the quiet motor (with noise less than 15db). Its hidden handle design enables easy movement to any desired location, making it an excellent choice for the whole family's home workouts.
Package Include: 1* ellipse leg exerciser equipment, 1*remote control(without 2 AAA batteries), 1*power cable, 2* foot straps, 1*Anti-slip PVC pad,1*user manual.

Ideal Gift Choice: This elliptical machine is an ideal holiday or birthday gift for friends, parents, or grandparents. It's a token of care for their health, fitting both fitness enthusiasts and those needing gentle exercise. Its user - friendly and compact design makes it a practical and thoughtful present.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Plate-loaded Leg Exercise Machine for Extensions and Curls 
Valor Fitness Plate Loaded Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine - Heavy Duty Hamstring & Quad Strengthening Equipment for Home Gym 
Elevate your lower body training with the Valor Fitness Plate Loaded Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine, designed to help you achieve stronger, more defined legs in the comfort of your home gym. This versatile, heavy-duty leg workout machine is engineered to target and promote muscle growth in your hamstrings, quadriceps, and calf muscles, enabling you to unlock your full potential. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced lifter, this machine offers an effective and adjustable solution to enhance your fitness goals and help you build strength, flexibility, and mobility. 
Maximize Your Lower Body Strength The Valor Fitness Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine allows you to isolate key muscle groups, focusing on the hamstrings and quadriceps for optimal muscle development. This machine enables you to perform leg curls and leg extensions with precision, increasing muscle definition and strength gains. By adding this equipment to your home gym, you can enhance your lower body workout routine, targeting muscles that are often neglected in other exercises. 
Versatile and Adjustable for Custom Workouts The adjustable thigh support ensures proper positioning and safety during leg curl exercises, providing maximum support for your legs and minimizing discomfort. This ensures your hamstrings and quads are working at their full potential during each rep. With the ability to load 1-inch Standard Plates or 2-inch Olympic Plates (using the Valor Fitness Olympic Adapter Sleeve, sold separately), this machine gives you the flexibility to tailor the weight to your personal strength level. Whether you're training for endurance, muscle toning, or building power, the plate-loaded design accommodates your needs and helps you achieve the perfect workout intensity. 
Designed for Safety and Stability The Valor Fitness Plate Loaded Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine is built for both safety and performance. The stable frame and secure thigh support keep you in the correct position throughout your leg curl and leg extension exercises, reducing the risk of injury while maximizing the effectiveness of your workout. This focus on injury prevention is crucial for athletes or anyone looking to improve joint health and flexibility in their lower body. 
Seamless Integration into Your Home Gym Not only does this adjustable leg machine provide exceptional performance, but it also blends seamlessly into any home gym environment. Its compact design makes it an excellent addition to small spaces, while its durable frame ensures it will withstand rigorous use for years to come. Whether you’re outfitting a home gym setup or a light-commercial gym, this heavy-duty machine will meet your fitness needs with ease, providing efficient strength training for all fitness levels. 
Why Choose the Valor Fitness Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine? 
Versatile Leg Workout: Target and strengthen your hamstrings, quadriceps, and calf muscles with a variety of exercises including leg curls and leg extensions. Perfect for enhancing leg strength, mobility, and flexibility.
Adjustable Design: Customizable to your preferred weightlifting style, this machine supports both 1-inch standard plates and 2-inch Olympic plates (Olympic adapter sleeve sold separately), giving you flexibility in your weight choice.
Durability and Stability: Built with a heavy-duty steel frame, this machine offers maximum stability and durability, ensuring a safe, smooth workout with every use.
Enhanced Performance: The adjustable thigh support ensures proper leg placement during exercises, allowing you to perform movements with maximum efficiency and muscle engagement.
Compact and Functional: This machine’s space-efficient design makes it perfect for home gym setups or small fitness areas, delivering professional-grade performance in any environment.
Achieve Your Lower Body Goals The Valor Fitness Plate Loaded Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine is more than just a piece of equipment; it’s a critical tool for achieving stronger, more resilient lower body muscles. By promoting hamstring and quadriceps isolation, it allows you to focus on muscle growth, flexibility, and joint health. Whether you're working toward muscle building, increased strength, or improved mobility, this machine will help you reach your fitness goals and maintain a healthy lower body. 
Take charge of your fitness journey today and unlock the full potential of your leg workouts with the Valor Fitness Plate Loaded Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine. Transform your lower body training with this powerful, adjustable machine, and see noticeable improvements in your strength and performance. 
Supercharge your leg workouts with the Valor Fitness Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine! Designed to maximize muscle growth in your hamstrings and calves, this versatile machine helps improve leg mobility and flexibility for a well-rounded lower body workout. 
Say goodbye to limited range of motion with the innovative Sun Dial adjuster, allowing you to easily customize settings and control the intensity of your workout. Featuring 8 adjustable positions for thigh support and 6 positions for back support, this machine adapts to your unique body size and exercise preferences for a truly personalized training experience. 
Safety and comfort are our top priorities. The adjustable thigh support ensures your legs stay securely in place during leg curl exercises, providing optimal performance while reducing the risk of injury. The backrest can be adjusted forward or backward to accommodate users of various heights, delivering a comfortable and ergonomic workout experience. 
This machine is compatible with 1-inch Standard Plates and 2-inch Olympic Plates for flexible weight options. For even more versatility, we offer the Valor Fitness Olympic Adapter Sleeve (sold separately), giving you the ability to increase weight and take your workouts to the next level. 
Built to withstand daily, intense use, the Valor Fitness Adjustable Leg Curl / Extension Machine is perfect for both home gyms and light-commercial settings. Its durable construction ensures long-lasting performance, making it an essential tool for achieving stronger, more defined legs. 
Upgrade your fitness routine and take your leg training to new heights with the Valor Fitness Leg Curl / Extension Machine—because you deserve more than mediocre workouts!

Fully Adjustable Leg Curl Machine 
Thigh support adjusts up or down in 8 positions and back support adjusts front or back in 6 positions to find the perfect support. 
Functional Fitness Machine 
Sundial adjustment allows the user to change the range of motion before performing leg curls or extensions. 
High Density Padded Rollers for Leg Comfort 
Comfortable, curved rollers keep the user firmly in place to isolate the muscle that’s being exercised while performing leg curls. Handles located on either side of the seat pad create additional support while performing extensions.

Why you need LE02 leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. LE02 leg extension machine is the best value for money. 
What is the most memorable point in LE02's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
What's the latest update point of LE02? 
You can change the leg extension machine to the leg curl machine with a simple plug. The removable thigh holder creates more training possibilities. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this leg machine contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Previous page
Next page
Why you need LE02 leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. LE02 leg extension machine is the best value for money. 
What is the most memorable point in LE02's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
What's the latest update point of LE02? 
You can change the leg extension machine to the leg curl machine with a simple plug. The removable thigh holder creates more training possibilities. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this leg machine contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.

2-in-1 Extension & Leg Curl Machine 
Get access to two of the most used lower body machines all in one compact piece of equipment. This strength training machine doubles as an extension machine and leg curl machine and features an easy pull pin to switch between the two in seconds. Add this machine to your home gym to pack some serious muscle onto your quads and hamstrings. Adjustable seat and thigh pads make this beast ideal for coaches and trainers working with multiple clients — or for anyone sharing a home gym with other users! 
ADJUSTABLE THIGH PAD 
An adjustable thigh pad lets you dial in on the movement you’re performing and increase the resistance to meet you where you’re at! 
ADJUSTABLE BACK REST 
The depth and angle of the supportive back rest can be adjusted so that users of every size are comfortable and supported. 
COUNTER-BALANCE POST 
A counter-balance weight post offers stability without permanent mounting — and makes for great extra weight plate storage for 2” Olympic plates! 
EASY PULL PIN 
This piece of equipment doubles as a leg extension and leg curl machine with the pull of a pin. That means you can switch between the two in seconds!

title: LIONSCOOL Leg Extension and Lying Leg Curl Machine, Adjustable Seated and Prone Lower Body Exercise Bench in Commercial Grade, Cable Operated Plate Loadable Leg Rotation Machine for Home Garage Gym
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: Commercial Grade for Home Gym & Garage Gym Use: Strong hamstrings and quadriceps are crucial for balance, speed and coordination. You'll wish every day was leg day with LIONSCOOL Leg Machine. Unique cable and pulley system supplies consistent resistance throughout the motions, which differs from traditional lever operated machine and assists with the growth of stronger and more defined muscles. It can be used for seated leg extension and lying leg curl. Only seated leg curl is not applicable.

Ultra Robust Structure with Rectangular Base and Extra Wide Foot Pads: The whole machine is constructed with 14-gauge tube and purpose built on a creative rectangular base to distribute pressure and eliminate rocking, ensuring an outstanding 400LBS weight plate loading capacity. And the weight capacity for users can reach up to 1000LBS. Each base foot has an enlarged stepped plate with a solid rubber covering, which increases stability further.

Tough Cable and Pulley Handle Great Weights: The steel cable is 8mm thick and will last through grueling workouts. We specially design an adjustable bolt to regulate tension in case the cable stretches out over the years. The pulley with an enhanced steel core can withstand heavier loads and more intensive training. Plate loading post measures 12” and fits 2-inch weight plates smoothly with its hard chrome plated surface.

Extreme Convenient with Open Seat and Adjustable Pads: We discard the impractical knee holder to make getting in and off the machine effortless and smooth. 6 seat depth adjustable backrest will accommodate users of all heights. Our self-adjusting foot roller with its 7 angles adjustable arm will conform to your leg position freely and the seat is quickly adjustable by one pull pin between seated and prone positions.

Innovative Seat Structure and Feel Comfort in Details: We have unique three-segment seat structure to maximize your comfort during your lying leg curls. The seat pad, middle pad and the backrest as well as the foam foot roller, are all 2.2” thick with high density EPE foam, combining firm support with gentle feel. All cushions feature textured PU surface to ensure anti-slip performance. And two pairs of rubber grip handles located on both sides help assist body stability.

Awesome Addition to Home Gym with Reliable Warranty: The assembled dimension is 45” width x 56” depth x 41” height to fit into your home gym. We offer Manufacturer Limited Warranty: 2 years on framework (structural steel & welds) and 1 year on other parts. Assembly instructions and wrenches will come with the machine. It is surely a cost-effective investment of your fitness equipment. Please note that this machine comes in two packages and may not arrive at the same time.

Why you need TT2S leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. 
What's the latest update point of TT2S? 
GMWD's engineers have changed the way weight holder is attached. Once again, the weighing capacity is increased and structural stability also level up. It's one step closer to the perfect leg day training machine. 
What is the most memorable point in TT2S's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this product contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Adjustable Leg Extension and Curl Machine – Independent Leg Isolation for Quadriceps and Hamstrings - Max Weight 330 lbs 
Independent Leg & Muscle Isolation: This machine allows you to work each leg independently or together, providing precise targeting of your quadriceps and hamstrings for optimal muscle isolation and growth.
Adjustable Design: With 6 back support positions and 9 thigh support adjustments, this machine also features a 15-position sundial and swivel shin pad to accommodate various body types for a comfortable and customizable workout.
Versatile Functionality: Effortlessly adjust the steel peg on the side of the frame to switch between leg extensions for your quadriceps and leg curls for your hamstrings, offering versatility for different exercises.
Additional Features: Compatible with both 1” and 2” weight plates (adaptor included), this machine supports a max weight capacity of 330 lbs (165 lbs per leg) for a challenging, effective workout.
Heavy-Duty Leg Machine with Dual Adjustable Sundial – Ideal for Leg Extensions and Curls 
The Heavy-Duty Leg Machine is designed to provide a durable and comfortable leg workout experience. Crafted from solid steel, it ensures long-lasting performance while the dual-layer vinyl padding offers maximum comfort during intense sessions. Convenient handles on both sides of the machine provide added support, allowing for secure and stable movements. With a machine weight of 132 lbs, it’s built for heavy-duty use. The dual adjustable sundial feature offers 15 adjustable positions, allowing users to target the quadriceps, hamstrings, and glutes with precision. Whether you're performing leg extensions or leg curls, this versatile machine supports a complete leg day workout, offering the flexibility to meet individual needs. Ideal for home gyms and commercial fitness spaces, this machine helps you build strength, improve muscle tone, and achieve your fitness goals with ease.
Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine with Single Leg Isolation Feature – Maximize Quadriceps and Hamstrings Development 
Step up your leg training with the Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine designed to enhance your strength training routine by isolating the quadriceps and hamstrings for maximum muscle growth and definition. Whether you’re aiming to build quad strength, improve hamstring flexibility, or correct muscle imbalances, this plate-loaded leg curl machine delivers the perfect solution. 
With a 330 lb weight capacity, this machine allows you to push your limits and build impressive leg muscles. The single leg extension isolation feature enables users to focus on one leg at a time, promoting symmetry and enhancing strength in both legs individually. This feature is especially beneficial for those recovering from injuries or wanting to address muscle imbalances. The independent leg movement also allows you to target hamstrings and quads with precision, ensuring an effective and tailored workout every time. 
Designed with durability in mind, the dual-layer vinyl padding offers both comfort and support throughout your workout. The thick padding helps reduce strain and discomfort, allowing you to focus on your form and performance. Whether you’re performing leg extensions or leg curls, the padding ensures a smooth and comfortable experience. Plus, the adjustable design allows you to customize the machine to your specific body type, ensuring you maintain proper alignment and posture throughout each movement. 
The Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine isn’t just limited to leg extensions or leg curls. Its versatile design allows you to perform a variety of lower body exercises targeting the quadriceps, hamstrings, glutes, and even your calves. You can switch between exercises quickly and easily, focusing on leg curls for hamstring development or leg extensions to isolate the quadriceps for a stronger, more defined lower body. 
By allowing you to work both legs simultaneously or isolating one leg at a time, this machine gives you the flexibility to tailor your workout routine to your goals. For example, single-leg isolation is ideal for rehabilitation exercises or for those looking to correct muscle imbalances between legs. It also aids in unilateral strength development, ensuring equal strength and muscle size in both legs. 
This leg extension machine is built to be compact and space-efficient, making it a perfect addition to any home gym or light-commercial fitness center. Despite its heavy-duty construction, it doesn’t take up a lot of floor space, making it ideal for those with limited workout room. The space-saving design allows you to keep your gym area organized without compromising on performance or functionality. 
Whether you are focusing on muscle development, strength training, or rehabilitation, this leg machine offers a reliable and efficient workout experience. It’s perfect for anyone looking to improve their lower body strength, enhance muscle definition, or address muscle imbalances in the quads and hamstrings. 
With a maximum weight capacity of 330 lbs, this leg machine is built to handle even the most intense weightlifting sessions. Whether you are performing light, high-repetition sets to tone your muscles or heavy sets for muscle mass, this machine can support your needs. The 330 lb weight capacity ensures that you can progressively increase the weight as you advance in your training, making it suitable for a variety of fitness levels, from beginners to advanced lifters. 
Safety and comfort are paramount when performing leg exercises, and this machine delivers both. The adjustable footrests and shin pads ensure proper positioning, while the adjustable thigh support accommodates different body sizes, allowing for a customizable workout. Additionally, the safety stops prevent any accidents if you are unable to complete a lift, ensuring a safe and secure exercise experience every time. 
Targeted Muscle Isolation: The machine's single leg extension feature allows for precise targeting of the quadriceps and hamstrings, promoting better strength, symmetry, and muscle development. Durable and Sturdy Construction: The solid steel frame ensures the machine can handle heavy loads and long-lasting use, providing stability and support during the most intense workouts. Versatile Lower Body Workouts: Whether you're performing leg extensions, leg curls, or focusing on single-leg isolation, this machine delivers a full leg day workout that targets all the major muscles in your legs. Comfortable and Safe: Dual-layer vinyl padding provides cushioning and comfort while performing each rep, while the adjustable design ensures proper form and safety during use. Perfect for Home and Commercial Use: The compact design fits easily in any home gym or commercial fitness space, while the high weight capacity supports a wide range of users and workout styles.

Ideal for home gyms or commercial fitness spaces, this machine is built for optimal muscle isolation and effective training. Enhance leg strength, improve muscle definition, and achieve your fitness goals with this adjustable leg equipment that delivers targeted results for your quadriceps and hamstrings. 
Heavy Duty Leg Day Machine – Solid Steel Construction with Dual Layer Vinyl Padding for Ultimate Comfort and Support 
The Heavy Duty Leg Day Machine is built for serious strength training, constructed from solid steel for maximum durability and stability during your toughest workouts. Featuring dual layer vinyl padding, this machine offers comfort and support, reducing strain during intense leg exercises. Convenient handles are positioned on both sides of the machine, providing added security and balance while performing leg extensions or curls. With a total machine weight of 132 lbs, this robust piece of equipment is designed to withstand heavy use in both home gyms and commercial fitness centers. Product Description
The DF807 Leg Extension / Leg Curl Machine by Deltech Fitness is a great way to shape your thighs and hamstring muscles. The super sturdy frame provide a stable, steady base and the fully adjustable leg pads provide versatility for users of all sizes. 
Built to last! 
The frame is made from heavy gauge steel tubing with a tough powdercoat finish. The seat and backrest pads are constructed of high density foam padding with a sweat resistant top grade vinyl that is easy to clean. 
Super stable! 
Sitting on heavy duty rubber feet, the DF807 Leg Extension/Leg Curl Machine provides a stable base for a safe and confident workout. 
Fully Adjustable! 
With fully adjustable leg pads on both leg curl and leg extension, the DF807 Leg Curl/Leg Extension Machine is designed for users of all sizes.
